title: Dak Prescott, Myles Garrett, Drew Brees, Derrick Henry
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Myles Garrett, Drew Brees, Derrick Henry
description:
Colin explains why Dak Prescott asking for too much hurt him in the end, why he feels the Cowboys offered Dak a fair deal, why he refuses to cancel players like Myles Garrett and Drew Brews, his thoughts on Derrick Henry's new contract, and the NFL position that is underpaid. Guests include Mark Dominik, Mike Fisher, Rob Parker, Joe Vardon, and Jason McIntyre.
